      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. i want to focus on the 'erosion of freedom' part. can you help me frame the critique that the 'harm principle' is basically just a loophole used by governments to justify whatever censorship they want? i want to show that there is no such thing as a 'safe' or 'balanced' amount of regulation without it becoming tyranny.",
